data.description: Looking for peaceful, private country living? This is it! Drive down the 300 ft. paved driveway & fall in love with this beautiful log home that's almost 5000 square feet. You can choose to enjoy the sounds & sights of nature on either the front or back porches that run the entire length of the house or the hot tub behind the big garage. The back yard overlooks a pond & wooded area, where I'm sure you'll see some wildlife. Inside, the open concept is breathtaking with the natural wood logs, which are insulated in between. You'll find the kitchen easy to work in & plenty of cabinet & counter space & an island for extra seating. 2 bedrooms on the 1st floor share a full bathroom & there's a half bath, too. The 2nd floor loft area can be used so many ways. You'll wake every morning & say goodnight from the primary bedroom that has sliding doors out to a big deck. The full bath has lots of closet space. On the other side of the house are 2 more bedrooms on the 2nd floor with beautiful views. The barn has 11 stalls, electric, water, tack & feed rooms. A nice big pasture for the animals to roam. A unique property that you can call home.
